after. The\n$f_{b,h}$-$M_h$ relation is unchanged in those cases as well, suggesting that\nthe Pop III formation rate for a given $M_h$ is insensitive to the tested\napproximations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2020 08:22:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jul 2020 10:06:19 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 11:37:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 3 Aug 2020 09:42:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-02"}
