anding of the dust and gas properties of\nhigh-redshift ($z\\gtrsim1$) star-forming galaxies during these first nine years\nof its science operations, and we highlight the interesting questions that may\nbe answered by ALMA in the years to come.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2020 11:07:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2021 12:10:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-18"}
