viously. In some parameter space\nregions, both candidates can produce a signal, therefore a double-line feature\narises as a smoking gun that would uncover the DM composition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Apr 2020 14:28:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-03"}
